    "synopsis": "After seven years of war, Horus's armada arrives in the Sol system and the long-prepared defence of Terra finally begins. Rogal Dorn's outer cordon stretches from Pluto inward — a screen of fortresses, void stations, and bled Imperial Navy squadrons meant not to win, but to slow the Warmaster long enough for the inner walls to be ready. Admiral Su-Kassen marshals what remains of the Sol fleet; Sigismund of the Imperial Fists seeks atonement in single combat; the remembrancer Mersadie Oliton looks for any way back to a Terra she may not recognise. On the traitor side, Abaddon executes Horus's plan as surely as Ahriman bends the warp around it. The first wall, in the void, falls hard.",
